10.3 Discoveries

fPosteriorPredictive <- function(numSamples, alpha, beta){
  X <- vector(length=numSamples)
  for(i in 1:numSamples){
    aLambda <- rgamma(1, alpha, beta)
    X[i] <-rpois(1, aLambda)
  }
return(X) 
  }
